  "detailed_description": "<strong>AR-K</strong> is a classical point and click adventure with an updated twist. <br><br><strong>IMPORTANT</strong>:This pack includes episodes 1 and 2 of AR-K<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>AR-K: Gone With The Sphere</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>AR-K: The Girl Who Wasn't There</li></ul><br>Episode 3 is now available on Steam!<br><u>AR-K: The Great Escape</u><br><br>Alicia Van Volish is a former cop and current journalism student who wakes up after a one-night stand with a terrible hangover and a lot of questions: How much did she drink? Did she really take that guy home with her? What was his name? And what, exactly, is the Golden Sphere, the mysterious object that seems the source of all Alicia’s woes?",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>AR-K</strong> is a classical point and click adventure with an updated twist. <br><br><strong>IMPORTANT</strong>:This pack includes episodes 1 and 2 of AR-K<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>AR-K: Gone With The Sphere</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>AR-K: The Girl Who Wasn't There</li></ul><br>Episode 3 is now available on Steam!<br><u>AR-K: The Great Escape</u><br><br>Alicia Van Volish is a former cop and current journalism student who wakes up after a one-night stand with a terrible hangover and a lot of questions: How much did she drink? Did she really take that guy home with her? What was his name? And what, exactly, is the Golden Sphere, the mysterious object that seems the source of all Alicia’s woes?",
